Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.02,0:00:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧 让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.85,0:00:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.16,0:00:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.19,0:00:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.25,0:00:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.26,0:00:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 还不能走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.38,0:00:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.19,0:00:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露乌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.68,0:00:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她直到最后…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.72,0:00:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.68,0:00:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都多亏了你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.94,0:00:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露乌…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.58,0:00:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.82,0:00:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.60,0:00:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和吉欧在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.82,0:00:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界也变得绚丽多彩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.75,0:00:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.67,0:01:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星移民计划
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.26,0:01:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因其失败被遗留在火星圈的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.45,0:01:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自称独立国家维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.04,0:01:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向地球联邦政府宣战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.00,0:01:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争开始 已将近70年
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------TXTA-------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.13,0:03:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是高达？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.57,0:03:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里怎么会有高达？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来吧 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音…难道是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你作为地球圈的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.65,0:03:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须亲眼见证维甘的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.46,0:03:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊泽尔坎特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的BOSS登场了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.02,0:03:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您快走 这里交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长快走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.81,0:03:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.81,0:03:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬间…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去吸引他的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.83,0:04:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在离开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.87,0:04:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是汇合坐标
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.01,0:04:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不快走！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.53,0:04:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来这里的目的就是救你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.43,0:04:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在 快走 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.43,0:04:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.22,0:04:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走啊 我马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.92,0:05:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上 锥炮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这台高达Legilis
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.44,0:05:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是对AGE-3进行分析研究
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并加入EXA-DB技术
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制造而成的新机体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在它面前没有胜算
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.69,0:06:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来吧 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有东西要让你看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在火星圈 遇到许多人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.27,0:06:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了维甘不全是坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.82,0:06:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球圈有很多人在等我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我不能回到你那里去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就和我战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.78,0:06:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打败我你才能回到地球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.15,0:06:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我…和你战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.63,0:06:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么天真无法幸存！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.73,0:07:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你见证了火星圈的悲惨现实
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该了解我们为何而战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要夺回地球
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.88,0:07:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且 质问那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是否有活着的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理解我一片苦心！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别听他的胡言乱语 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊泽尔坎特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您没事吧 伊泽尔坎特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 放心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.41,0:08:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的存在太过危险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是现在就干掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.48,0:08:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没有那种必要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.35,0:08:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达和吉欧 我都要活捉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.63,0:08:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止吧 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖投降对你有好处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.91,0:08:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.18,0:08:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是一个人在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.29,0:08:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续射击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.84,0:08:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但凡包围圈这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微在哪里戳它一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会轻易垮掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我使劲打
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.07,0:08:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.49,0:08:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去歼灭碍事的海盗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊泽尔坎特大人的命令必须遵守
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的对手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,省省吧 才没那种心情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然想这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.85,0:09:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有选择了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.54,0:09:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊泽尔坎特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再做这种事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.69,0:09:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会告诉地球上的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.46,0:09:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星圈的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以发动战争
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非想让维甘的人民移居地球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有打算歼灭地球种
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.01,0:09:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里告诉你 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:09:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的计划 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.21,0:10:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是伊甸计划的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.27,0:10:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸…计划？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.71,0:10:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从世界上出现人类的那一刻起就有战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有限的资源和有限的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.08,0:10:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为争夺这些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.87,0:10:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类反复上演着鲜血书写的历史
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.89,0:10:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去人类终有一天会自取灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我精心准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为创造一个绝对不存在争斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由贤明的人类所组成的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在极限环境下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.62,0:10:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同人的大脑和身体能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到DNA序列支配
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会采取不同的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.51,0:10:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在调查的基础上鉴别出更优秀的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之所以袭击诺拉和安琪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.85,0:10:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是为营造出极限环境
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:10:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在维甘的卫星中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.91,0:11:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也曾伪装成事故 制造过相同的情形
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.42,0:11:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.19,0:11:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为选出能担负起人类新时代重任的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.53,0:11:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更优秀的种群
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.57,0:11:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为创造没有战争的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.41,0:11:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为创造安宁与和平的理想乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创造伊甸！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.41,0:11:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.47,0:11:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不分维甘与联邦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:11:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有优秀种群可以在那里生活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.60,0:12:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是那个乐园的建立者！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------TXTB-------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.56,0:12:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 这么纤细的缆索
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妄想困住Zamdrug！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的只是让你停下一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.02,0:12:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个挺有意思的对手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为海盗来说！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙硬得就像块臭石头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大副 这样下去危险
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.43,0:13:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道 让他们给我顶住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.33,0:13:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有几分钟？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.58,0:13:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.63,0:13:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死 都怪那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.97,0:13:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为它 把我们的计划全打乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.64,0:13:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要做这么残忍的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为救人类逃脱灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过鉴别优秀的种群
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从此使战乱在人类的历史中消失！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.55,0:13:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么那些没有被选中的人怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:13:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在实现伟大理想的过程中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.57,0:14:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牺牲是不可避免的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.33,0:14:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维甘的人们呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.79,0:14:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们那么信任你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狄恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.58,0:14:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和露乌都那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也失去了罗米
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.67,0:14:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我自己所剩的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻 决不能沉浸于一时的悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.69,0:14:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想像下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居住在一个没有争斗的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.94,0:14:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们会心的微笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是… 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.13,0:14:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我毕生追求的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.07,0:15:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.89,0:15:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉德克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.78,0:15:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射出G-Scepter
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.14,0:15:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.16,0:15:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G-Scepter？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要亲手打开…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:16:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通往新世界的大门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.08,0:16:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人人都能活得有尊严！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.93,0:16:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 罗米
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.58,0:16:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球是个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.54,0:16:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么样的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.68,0:16:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈也没去过那里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没法告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.15,0:16:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗米
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如果转世投胎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想生在地球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.61,0:16:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想要你们做我的爸爸妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.85,0:16:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我们一起在地球上生活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.08,0:16:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗米
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.86,0:17:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.91,0:17:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是他的转世
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是他转世投胎重新回到我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.62,0:17:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不明白我的苦衷！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不会是唯一的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.84,0:17:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用发动战争也有其他办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都是你的想像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.55,0:17:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,历史证明了人类无法斩断暴力的链锁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.44,0:17:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达跟不上我的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没好吗 拉德克
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.21,0:18:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大副 准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 接通信号
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.44,0:18:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.29,0:18:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即停止战斗行为
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.32,0:18:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复 立即停止战斗行为
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.25,0:18:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.91,0:18:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不满足我们的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.44,0:19:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让这些小行星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砸向你们的殖民地 月亮二号
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.12,0:19:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.54,0:19:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙小人！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.58,0:19:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 敌众我寡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.93,0:19:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是迫不得已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧我带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.19,0:19:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 船长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.64,0:19:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就剩你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.33,0:19:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,180度调头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.88,0:19:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时最大战速
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.82,0:19:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我撤！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.95,0:20:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 把它们给忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.98,0:20:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夹带着干扰物的虚拟气球？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.23,0:20:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太看不起人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.65,0:20:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追！不能让他们活着回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.17,0:20:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在追击也为时已晚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全军返航
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.91,0:20:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.49,0:20:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有听见我的命令吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.77,0:20:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不敢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.92,0:20:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说当时就应该干掉高达
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.45,0:20:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.01,0:20:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活该 维甘这些傻瓜吃瘪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:21:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样他们也该瞑目了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.31,0:21:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么哭丧着脸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大副
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.75,0:21:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备酒宴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.73,0:21:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是一群朝不保夕的亡命之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.61,0:21:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝酒庆祝才是最合适的悼念方式
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.11,0:21:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.79,0:21:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.32,0:21:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为选出能担负起人类新时代重任的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.73,0:21:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更优秀的种群
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.61,0:21:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为创造没有战争的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.37,0:21:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为创造安宁与和平的理想乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.83,0:21:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创造伊甸！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.94,0:21:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我毕生追求的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.06,0:21:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该…怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.14,0:22:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎加入我军
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.27,0:22:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇敢的维甘战士们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.30,0:22:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如你们所知
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.11,0:22:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人已经进犯月亮二号
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.66,0:22:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗必将十分惨烈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.74,0:22:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期待你们的勇气！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.17,0:22:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
